  <brief_title>Satisfaction in Patients Receiving the PegIntron Pen Plus Rebetol for Hepatitis C (Study P04244)(COMPLETED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Satisfaction in Patients Receiving PegIntron Pen/Rebetol for Hepatitis C in Slovenia</official_title>
